# operating on Walter Benjamin
Consider this original essay from Walter Benjamin, [[The Work of Art in the Age of Mechanical Reproduction.]] How might we use artificial intelligence to operate on it? To 'update' it in new context with new references and new opportunities?
- [[Semantic Zooming]] Using GPT-3.5 summarization to re-read "The Work of Art in the Age of Mechanical Reproduction" at varying levels of detail
- [[The Work of Art in the Age of Generative AI]] rewriting the same essay in the context of generative AI
- [[The Work of Art in the Age of Generative AI, 0.02]] rewriting again, some variations.
- [[The Work of Art in the Age of Generative AI 0.03]] scrubbed through GPT-4
